title: "Boatman Sinking Boat": Jharkhand Congress Minister Slams Own Government - NDTV
content: "Boatman Sinking Boat": Jharkhand Congress Minister Slams Own Government  NDTVView Full coverage on Google News
description: Jharkhand Health Minister and Congress leader Banna Gupta on Tuesday alleged that the Chief Minister and Jharkhand Mukti Morcha (JMM) leader Hemant Soren wants to weaken the Congress and capture its voter base.
